title: Memory Game Pack [Android] [.apk]
description:
GAME PACK CONTAINS:
------------------------------------

----
Forest Memory Game:

Forest Memory Game is a free game addressed to the younger players.
Using the touchscreen smartphone or tablet, player tries to match a pair of the same animals.

Features
* Non-violent game - safe for kids.
* A good workout for the mind.
* English and Polish language version.
* Over 30 different kinds of animals.
* 10 amazing colorful levels.
* Medals for achievements in the game.
* List of the top players from around the world.
* Support devices with different screens (2.7-10.1 inches).


----
Picnic Memory Game:

Picnic Memory Game is a free game addressed to the younger players.
Using the touch screen smartphone or tablet, player tries to match a pair of the same food - snacks. For each pair player receive points which can be spent in the shop.

Features
* Non-violent game - safe for kids.
* Charming graphic.
* A good workout for the mind.
* English and Polish language version.
* Over 20 different kinds of food.
* 5 amazing colorful levels.
* Medals for achievements in the game.
* List of the top players from around the world.
* Relaxing music
* Support devices with different screens (2.7-10.1 inches).
